data.description: As soon as you step foot into the entryway of this adorable home you are welcomed with charm and cozy vibes which is sure to make you want this home as your very own! It  consists of an open concept throughout the living room, dining area and kitchen. There are three bedrooms and two bathrooms as well as a modern kitchen with stainless steel appliances. This home also includes a bonus area that can be utilized as office space! Lets not forget the back deck that will be the perfect place to enjoy a cup of coffee as well as the cool fall air!! Do not let this opportunity pass you by as this home will not last long!! All showings to start on 10/9/2023. Interior pics coming soon!
